-- Bulgaria's GERB party says difficult to form government 
-- By Tsvetelia Tsolova
-- Sun Oct 05, 2014 01:26PM EDT
-- None



SOFIA, Oct 5 (Reuters) - The fractured result of the Bulgarian election will make forming a government difficult, but the centre-right GERB party will hold internal discussions on Monday to decide on how to proceed, GERB's leader said on Sunday.

